    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This can be fixed by giving the E3 a garrisoned weapon that has a horizontal rate of turn of 255:\r\n\r\ninfantry.yaml:\r\nE3:\r\n+Armament@GARRISONED:\r\n+Name: garrisoned\r\n+Weapon: Dragon.garrisoned\r\n\r\nmissiles.yaml:\r\nDragon.garrisoned\r\n+Inherits: Dragon\r\n+Projectile: Missile\r\n++HorizontalRateOfTurn: 255"
